SLi2sBGDKvY.title: Truffle Ice Cream · Procrema 100 Cold · Texturizers
SLi2sBGDKvY.description:
Ingredients:
 
900 gr. Milk 
50   gr. Sugar 
75   gr. Liquid glucose
100 gr. ProCrema 100 cold
50   gr. Glycerin
50   gr. Truffle
2     gr.  Salt

Process:
Combine liquid ingredients on one hand and solids on the other
Mix both parts and blend the mixture with an immersion blender
Let in the fridge for 3 hours
Mix again the mixture
Put in the ice cream machine

TMCoSFOQpec.title: 【踏切】珍！珍！風景！ 大津里道踏切道
TMCoSFOQpec.description:
島根県出雲市にある大津里道踏切は、一畑電車とＪＲ山陰本線が共用する２箇所の踏切の一つです。
列車が通過する際の踏切警報機の動作が一畑電車とＪＲの列車で異なるという珍しいものとなっています。

踏切警報機は、ＪＲ側と一畑側で一機ずつそれぞれの会社が管理しており、表示機器や警報音などに違いが観られます。
中でも、映像当初の奥側にあるＪＲが管理する警報機は、同社管理のものとしては非常に珍しい電鈴を装備する警報機となっています。

大津里道踏切
ＪＲ山陰本線　直江～出雲市
一畑電車今市線　出雲科学館パークタウン前～大津町
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2014.7追記
この踏切道は2014年6月に道路部分の拡幅が施され、その際に踏切警報器、遮断機などの設備が全て更新され、懐かしい電鈴は無くなり電子音に統一、[電車]表記は[一畑]へ、[汽車]表記は[JR]へそれぞれ変わりました。
----------------------------------------------------------
2018.1.23 再生回数が10,000,000回を超えました。たくさんの御視聴誠にありがとうございます。

aK_BovnXzeo.title: All-Access: NBA All-Star Relay
aK_BovnXzeo.description:
To highlight the importance of physical activity and promote healthy living for kids and families, the NBA teamed up with New York Road Runners (NYRR) for the first-ever marathon relay.   Twenty-four runners, including NBA & WNBA Legends, broadcasters and league executives teamed with NYRR Youth Running Ambassadors to pass the baton over the 26.2-mile tour of New York City’s five boroughs during the TCS NYC Marathon on November 2nd.

About the NBA: 
The NBA is the premier professional basketball league in the United States and Canada. ZeLvjQbmMXk.title: Unforgotten Realms Episode 46
ZeLvjQbmMXk.description:
Unforgotten Realms was a video series created in 2009. It was written, voiced, animated by myself originally for Escapist Magazine. While a few episodes were made after Escapist Magazine abandoned the show, it was never finished.

While some would wish me to return to this series from where it left off, it would not be the same. I have grown and changed so much since I worked on this project that anything less than another reboot would be a disservice. When the time comes that I am at a point in my life where I can focus on nothing but this show and I have the money and people to create it exactly the way I always wanted, I will revisit and recreate this once more for you guys. For those of you wondering about the "ending" I can honestly tell you that I never really decided how to end this show, it never felt like it should have an ending, but I'm sorry if that's not good enough after you invested yourself into 50 episodes.

The show uses some language that at the time felt a bit more appropriate and acceptable. Words like Fag and Faggot are used playfully and not meant to hurt. Funny enough, while the series is written for adult audiences, it avoids using words like Fuck. In this way, it's very much dated, but please know the use of language was never meant to insult (and apologies to those watching years later when I came to realize how hurtful they could be.)

Please enjoy the hard work of a younger me. I look forward to the day I can return to this series.
